{"tid":2112350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2020-07-17 本港二手樓價連續兩周上升","createTime":"2020-07-17T08:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T08:53:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa9bd6bd68b3f2f801c0722baf857eb1725083c","tid":2112350,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538364-20200717.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538364-20200717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=1c8dce9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538364-20200717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f4e8ecd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538364-20200717.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n反映本港二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數報180.81，按周升1.04%，連續兩周上升。大型屋苑指數、中小型單位指數同大型單位指數都升。<br />\n<br />\n按地區計，只有新界西微跌0.01%，其餘3區都升。<br />\n<br />\n今日公布的指數涉及的交易有80%在上月22日至28日簽訂臨時買賣協議。"}]}